data.description: Come take a look at this gorgeous home in Desert Ridge. Close proximity to freeway access and all grade schools nearby. 3 bed 2 bath POOL home ready for new owners. New carpet, new paint, and new Kitchen appliances. Enjoy the spacious kitchen for entertaining! Double Gates, and extra parking space. Lots of cabinets and storage throughout the home. Super well kept home. PAID OFF SOLAR PANELS.
